            Whether by air, sea, or ground, our freight services handle shipments
            of all sizes. From pallets to full containers, we provide reliable
            and cost-effective solutions for your cargo needs.
          </p>
          <ul class="service-features">
            <li>Air freight for urgent cargo</li>
            <li>Sea freight for bulk shipments</li>
            <li>Ground freight nationwide</li>
            <li>Full and partial load options</li>
            <li>Customs clearance support</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="service-visual">
          <div class="visual-card green">
            <span class="card-number">50+</span>
            <span class="card-label">Countries Connected</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Warehousing -->
      <div class="service-block" id="warehouse">
        <div class="service-content">
          <span class="service-icon-large">üè≠</span>
          <h3>Warehousing & Storage</h3>
          <p>
            Our state-of-the-art warehousing facilities provide secure storage
            and efficient inventory management. With strategic locations and
            advanced systems, we keep your goods safe and accessible.
          </p>
          <ul class="service-features">
            <li>Climate-controlled storage</li>
            <li>Inventory management system</li>
            <li>Pick and pack services</li>
            <li>Cross-docking capabilities</li>
            <li>24/7 security monitoring</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="service-visual">
          <div class="visual-card gold">
            <span class="card-number">15</span>
            <span class="card-label">Strategic Locations</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Last Mile -->
      <div class="service-block reverse" id="lastmile">
        <div class="service-content">
          <span class="service-icon-large">üì¶</span>
          <h3>Last Mile Delivery</h3>
          <p>
            The final stretch matters most. Our last mile delivery service ensures
            your packages reach their destination safely and on time, with options
            for residential and commercial deliveries.
          </p>
          <ul class="service-features">
            <li>Residential delivery</li>
            <li>Commercial delivery</li>
            <li>Flexible time windows</li>
            <li>Contactless delivery options</li>
            <li>Photo proof of delivery</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="service-visual">
          <div class="visual-card red">
            <span class="card-number">99.8%</span>
            <span class="card-label">Success Rate</span>
