          <p>End-to-end supply chain management.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="add-service-card">
          <span class="add-icon">üåø</span>
          <h4>Green Shipping</h4>
          <p>Eco-friendly delivery options available.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="add-service-card">
          <span class="add-icon">üè¢</span>
          <h4>Business Solutions</h4>
